		<div class="quote"><p>@Chris: you raise an interesting point. Likewise, I don't believe that you can use the stats off your own site to base design decisions on as current audience isn't necessarily reflective of future audience. As they say, there are lies, damned lies and statistics.</p>
<p>It'd still be interesting to see that kind of info. I'm a bit of a stats junkie and think that even some relevancy can be pulled out of it. I just wouldn't put my life on it.
</p>
</div>
